<i>Something was there.</i>

01:19.010 --> 01:22.570
<i>Lurking in the stretching
darkness.</i>

01:29.320 --> 01:30.550
<i>Don't touch the bag.</i>

01:32.820 --> 01:34.260
<i>We're fucked.</i>

01:34.960 --> 01:36.290
<i>We've got customers.</i>

01:37.390 --> 01:38.550
<i>They called the cops?</i>

01:38.930 --> 01:40.090
<i>What happened?</i>

01:40.400 --> 01:42.230
The operation was kept
confidential.

01:43.530 --> 01:44.330
Yeah.

01:46.300 --> 01:48.360
I'm telling now 'cause
I just found out.

01:49.470 --> 01:50.730
Who's on?

01:51.510 --> 01:52.410
Beom-soo.

01:53.540 --> 01:54.840
<i>Can you get him off?</i>

01:57.810 --> 01:58.970
We'll try.

02:01.980 --> 02:03.280
We've got cops on board.

02:07.360 --> 02:10.190
Why do parents take
their children for granted?

02:16.930 --> 02:18.760
I'll give it to you for $1.

02:18.900 --> 02:21.530
Just a single dollar
If you look here...

02:21.600 --> 02:23.500
Hey, mister, can I take
a look at that?

02:23.570 --> 02:26.130
Of course. If you look here,
the blade is...

02:30.110 --> 02:32.140
Hey... Throw the knife away.

02:37.450 --> 02:38.390
Hey, is that a gun?

02:38.520 --> 02:41.510
Shit, let's just jump him.

02:49.000 --> 02:50.970
There's just one bullet left!

02:51.600 --> 02:52.790
Aw, shit.

02:57.710 --> 02:58.700
Hey, don't lose it!

03:09.620 --> 03:12.140
Hey, asshole!
Let go of him!

03:17.460 --> 03:18.760
Come over here! Quick!

03:25.670 --> 03:27.030
Get... get behind me...

03:50.360 --> 03:51.790
Oh, I'm sorry...

03:53.400 --> 03:54.390
This is nicely sharpened.

03:56.200 --> 03:57.220
Real sharp.

04:12.410 --> 04:15.680
Beom-soo's a lazy bum,
but he makes one hell of a gun.

04:15.780 --> 04:17.450
You should've seen
those cops' faces.

04:17.519 --> 04:19.649
Is that a gun? Is that a gun?

04:26.130 --> 04:27.490
Buh... bury it?

04:28.930 --> 04:30.260
Buh... but it's still alive!

04:30.600 --> 04:33.190
It's all withered.

04:34.370 --> 04:35.500
No good anymore.

04:36.810 --> 04:39.930
Let's end things here.
It's just too risky.

04:40.380 --> 04:44.440
If they hear he's still alive
they'll definitely... pay up.

04:44.650 --> 04:45.740
Won't they?

04:51.290 --> 04:52.720
This is so not my style.

05:00.300 --> 05:01.520
That's for me to decide.

05:03.770 --> 05:04.630
Got it?

05:09.500 --> 05:11.740
Thuh... then... we're good,
right?

05:20.120 --> 05:22.520
Aw... he's throwing up.
Is... is he sick?

05:23.990 --> 05:26.010
I'm telling you it's gone bad...

05:26.990 --> 05:29.290
Aw... gross!

05:29.760 --> 05:31.020
Young-joo!

05:31.230 --> 05:32.350
Come here for a sec!

05:35.530 --> 05:37.500
Peek-a-boo!

05:42.300 --> 05:44.770
Oh, Young-joo!

05:50.010 --> 05:51.500
He... he's cute...

05:54.050 --> 05:57.310
Whuh... what should we
call him?

05:57.390 --> 05:58.940
<i>SPRING 1998</i>

06:01.760 --> 06:05.060
<i>This afternoon, a gang of
masked robbers hit a bank...</i>

06:05.260 --> 06:07.060
<i>The police are searching
for the suspects...</i>

06:07.230 --> 06:10.560
<i>Unrevealing their faces and
dodging surveillance cameras...</i>

06:10.730 --> 06:12.060
<i>Their nickname, Day Breakers</i>

06:12.170 --> 06:16.000
<i>came from their daring capers...
during broad daylight.</i>

06:16.100 --> 06:19.070
<i>A warehouse robbery today...</i>

06:19.140 --> 06:20.770
<i>Nevertheless, their trademark...</i>

06:20.840 --> 06:24.110
<i>untraceable work,
handmade weapons...</i>

06:24.210 --> 06:27.940
<i>and unusual crime technique
are baffling the police...</i>

06:28.080 --> 06:32.820
<i>The Day Breakers case is
shocking the nation.</i>

06:33.150 --> 06:38.350
<i>A community credit coop
was raided by armed...</i>

07:15.830 --> 07:20.530
<i>HWAYI: A MONSTER BOY</i>

07:27.010 --> 07:30.670
You're as good as they say.

07:37.520 --> 07:39.950
What happened to your eyes?

07:41.320 --> 07:42.920
I was born like this.

07:43.160 --> 07:46.290
Then, you've never seen
anything your entire life?

07:47.700 --> 07:50.790
I can actually see
things close up.

07:55.900 --> 07:58.340
Are you expecting someone, sir?

07:58.610 --> 07:59.370
Huh?

08:01.710 --> 08:03.470
I can hear someone outside.

08:07.980 --> 08:09.380
I can't hear a thing.

08:09.880 --> 08:11.880
But someone's here...

08:11.990 --> 08:13.680
They're here...

08:13.890 --> 08:15.880
Who... who the hell
are you?

08:21.560 --> 08:22.690
And, done!

08:22.860 --> 08:23.700
Hey!

08:24.330 --> 08:28.270
Hey! Do you know who I am,
you fucking crooks?

08:28.340 --> 08:29.070
I know!

08:30.000 --> 08:31.100
Open it.

08:31.510 --> 08:35.030
Bribe money's gotta be laundered
ASAP 'cause everyone knows now.

08:35.309 --> 08:36.840
It's just some silly rumor.

08:39.510 --> 08:40.610
I'll do it, I'll do it!

08:41.480 --> 08:43.280
But...

08:43.990 --> 08:45.080
It's actually this hand.

08:51.130 --> 08:54.620
Think wisely. 'Cause I'm not
in the mood for liars.

08:55.530 --> 08:57.260
I'm not lying.

08:59.530 --> 09:00.930
It's this hand, this one.

09:02.570 --> 09:03.200
Open it.

09:17.220 --> 09:18.520
Hey you motherfuckers!

09:19.220 --> 09:21.250
You shouldn't have
underestimated me.

09:21.320 --> 09:22.920
Consider this your lucky day.

09:23.090 --> 09:25.080
I'm not in the mood for trouble.
So get the hell out!

09:25.730 --> 09:26.850
Don't you get it?

09:27.300 --> 09:30.160
Since I haven't seen your faces,
just beat it!

09:34.100 --> 09:35.040
Now you've seen me.

09:36.270 --> 09:37.030
Kill him.

09:38.740 --> 09:40.000
May I?

09:40.270 --> 09:41.140
Yes, kill him.

09:44.780 --> 09:45.940
Yuck! Shit...

09:46.610 --> 09:47.950
Hey, he's dead! Dead!

09:48.950 --> 09:50.150
What a fucking psycho.

09:51.520 --> 09:54.050
You sure know how to hit
the right spot.

10:04.770 --> 10:06.200
<i>SUNGJI (HOLY LAND)</i>

10:06.630 --> 10:07.800
So you really can't see a thing?

10:10.840 --> 10:11.670
I... I can't...

10:16.540 --> 10:17.710
Whatcha doin?

10:18.180 --> 10:20.150
Aren't ya gonna kill him?

10:20.780 --> 10:21.840
There he goes again...

10:23.250 --> 10:24.810
When the cops come, remember.

10:26.290 --> 10:28.950
You never saw ME,
but I saw YOU.

10:29.360 --> 10:30.120
Okay?

10:35.560 --> 10:37.190
Hurry up!

10:45.710 --> 10:46.830
Hurry, get up close!

10:54.480 --> 10:56.180
Hey, which way did they go?

10:57.350 --> 10:59.250
- Hey, to the left, to the left!
- Aw, shit!

11:19.040 --> 11:21.700
<i>WINTER 2012</i>

12:05.720 --> 12:08.250
Hey, school boy!
Can you lend me a hand?

12:15.630 --> 12:17.100
I've seen you a few times.

12:17.300 --> 12:18.390
You live around here,
don't you?

12:21.200 --> 12:23.360
Which school wears that uniform?

12:27.040 --> 12:29.410
I guess you don't wanna
talk to me, right?

13:00.270 --> 13:02.300
Hey, school boy,
what's your name?

13:08.620 --> 13:09.240
Hwayi...

13:10.890 --> 13:11.680
My name is Hwayi.

13:12.620 --> 13:13.250
Hwayi?

13:14.890 --> 13:16.150
What an unusual name.

13:19.130 --> 13:21.600
Bye, Hwayi!
Thanks for the orange!

13:34.840 --> 13:37.330
Why kill him when he couldn't
call the cops anyway?

13:38.410 --> 13:42.250
That dude's morally fucked up.
He's just a crook.

13:42.620 --> 13:44.090
But he's an ex-prosecutor.

13:44.450 --> 13:46.350
This could get us in deep shit.

13:49.220 --> 13:50.160
You...

13:50.990 --> 13:53.990
should've finished the job.
Why let the other guy go?

13:54.730 --> 13:57.100
Why do you have to do
things on a whim?

13:57.400 --> 13:59.590
- What's the use of planning...
- Enough, I get it.

14:03.670 --> 14:05.440
Wasn't this the plan anyway?

14:36.370 --> 14:39.900
That crook stashed so much
for himself it's hard counting.

14:56.260 --> 14:57.320
Let's go to the
public bathhouse later.

14:59.290 --> 14:59.950
I don't want to.

15:02.230 --> 15:03.490
What's the big deal?

15:12.040 --> 15:12.840
Shit!

15:14.880 --> 15:16.280
Little twerp.

15:17.180 --> 15:19.410
- I'm home.
- Hey!

15:20.010 --> 15:20.640
Hwuh, Hwayi

15:21.050 --> 15:24.610
Whi, which way did you come?
I... I kept watching for you.

15:25.620 --> 15:26.420
The orchard.

15:26.490 --> 15:29.550
You should've called me.
Whuh, why bother walking?

15:29.660 --> 15:30.390
Son!

15:31.330 --> 15:32.420
Great job today.

15:33.660 --> 15:34.790
You deserve this.

15:35.000 --> 15:37.990
Duh... don't give too much
muh... money to the kid.

15:38.270 --> 15:42.130
A real man should have
a fat pocket, right?

15:43.700 --> 15:45.070
This will make my pocket
fat enough.

15:45.370 --> 15:46.670
Any problems on the way?

15:47.440 --> 15:48.200
No, dad.

15:48.480 --> 15:49.500
Good job today.

15:52.680 --> 15:53.580
Yes, father.

15:54.550 --> 15:56.880
Fruh, from now on,
call me, okay?

16:13.370 --> 16:15.230
Did I ever mention I was
craving for this?

16:16.670 --> 16:19.370
No, but they're your favorite
anyway.

16:21.480 --> 16:23.340
Let's split one. Wait...

16:39.260 --> 16:42.160
Hey, Beom-soo. What did you
do to the bullet?

16:43.300 --> 16:45.700
- Did he hit it? Let me see.
- Nice... He totalled it.

17:08.119 --> 17:11.560
Nice! We should get him
into the Olympics.

17:11.690 --> 17:14.319
It looks like our son's
great at everything.

17:14.400 --> 17:16.300
- Stop practicing...
- Let's eat.

17:18.069 --> 17:20.359
Come here. Come, Hwayi.

17:20.430 --> 17:23.670
But Beom-soo, where would
we use these bullets?

17:23.869 --> 17:25.810
Korea's all about blades.

17:26.040 --> 17:28.810
Hwayi, let's have a blade fight
after dinner, okay?

17:29.440 --> 17:32.880
<i>Suk-tae's getting more
fucked up with age.</i>

17:33.250 --> 17:36.080
<i>He's getting more and more
crazier.</i>

17:37.050 --> 17:39.750
<i>He should think of the people
cleaning up after his shit.</i>

17:40.620 --> 17:42.780
<i>He can't go on shitting
all over my territory...</i>

17:42.860 --> 17:43.590
What about the blind guy?

17:43.960 --> 17:47.990
<i>Who cares? He's scared shitless
but you never know.</i>

17:48.960 --> 17:51.690
<i>In my opinion,
Suk-tae has no vision.</i>

17:52.400 --> 17:54.130
<i>You and I need to be swimming
in bigger waters.</i>

17:55.940 --> 17:59.270
<i>Hey! Want me to fix you up
with Mr. JEON from Incheon?</i>

17:59.610 --> 18:00.340
Who?

18:00.710 --> 18:02.940
<i>You know, Mr. JEON Seung-ki
from Incheon.</i>

18:03.540 --> 18:04.670
<i>Now that's a man with a vision!</i>

18:06.150 --> 18:08.980
You call that vision? It's just
gangsters doing business.

18:10.580 --> 18:13.990
He's not the same man
you used to know.

18:14.260 --> 18:16.690
<i>He's handling all the big
redevelopment projects</i>

18:17.960 --> 18:19.690
<i>in the metropolitan area.</i>

18:20.330 --> 18:23.560
The dude is now holding the,
veins of Korea.

18:23.960 --> 18:24.730
You don't say?

18:25.200 --> 18:29.600
They're on a redevelopment
project in our district.

18:30.600 --> 18:35.070
But one house is giving them
a headache 'cause they won't budge.

18:35.940 --> 18:38.310
How about removing them?

18:39.010 --> 18:40.780
We're no mercenary gangsters.

18:41.250 --> 18:45.650
They've already tried that
shit on these people.

18:46.590 --> 18:47.560
Breaking.

18:48.220 --> 18:49.420
Threatening.

18:50.160 --> 18:51.060
Torching.

18:53.930 --> 18:57.760
But they just won't budge.
And legally they have the right.

18:59.030 --> 19:00.300
We have no other choice

19:01.640 --> 19:02.530
but... to kill them off.

19:03.770 --> 19:06.540
So, why won't these people
move out?

19:07.470 --> 19:08.870
That's the fucked up part.

19:09.940 --> 19:11.540
IM Hyung-taek lives there.

19:12.010 --> 19:13.880
Who? LEE Myung-taek?

19:14.150 --> 19:16.980
No you moron, IM Hyung-taek,
the owner of Sungji Cement!

19:18.990 --> 19:21.150
<i>You can go wild
on your asking price.</i>

19:21.790 --> 19:23.990
<i>And if the job's done well,</i>

19:24.890 --> 19:28.160
<i>you'll get your network with
Mr. JEON and your vision.</i>

19:28.300 --> 19:30.130
<i>- How about it? Are you in?
- Hey...</i>

19:31.070 --> 19:34.500
I'm a bit busy now.
Let's talk later.

19:34.570 --> 19:37.730
<i>Busy? Are you kidding me?
What the fuck...</i>

19:41.580 --> 19:43.010
You're not busy at all...

19:54.920 --> 19:58.290
After a 3 month language course,
you can start school.

19:59.990 --> 20:01.050
And this too.

20:04.600 --> 20:06.730
Memorize the name
and date of birth.

20:08.470 --> 20:10.600
Basic things, that
I'll take care of,

20:11.540 --> 20:15.530
but for the time being...
you're on your own, okay?

20:19.110 --> 20:20.240
Okay. I'll talk to him.

20:20.680 --> 20:23.280
<i>Trust me. You'll regret this bad
if you don't do this.</i>

20:23.550 --> 20:24.610
I'll leave you two to talk.

20:33.190 --> 20:33.850
What's going on?

20:38.830 --> 20:40.300
I'm going out.

20:42.170 --> 20:43.070
Where to?

20:43.940 --> 20:44.730
Downtown.

20:49.040 --> 20:50.640
You're going out quite
often these days.

20:51.810 --> 20:53.110
Are you wearing that again?

20:55.020 --> 20:56.040
I prefer this.

20:56.480 --> 20:57.510
'Cause it doesn't stand out.

20:59.320 --> 21:00.650
You've grown again.

21:06.290 --> 21:07.190
So he wants to go?

21:09.430 --> 21:11.760
We should let him go.
It's what we agreed on.

21:15.100 --> 21:16.090
Did we?

21:19.340 --> 21:20.900
We can't keep him here like this.

21:21.910 --> 21:23.840
Hwayi's different from us.

21:24.450 --> 21:25.280
Different...

21:29.020 --> 21:30.780
You used to be different,

21:31.520 --> 21:32.250
weren't you?

21:35.820 --> 21:37.380
So what's his excuse
for staying?

21:38.260 --> 21:39.280
That IM Hyung-taek?

21:49.840 --> 21:53.000
<i>SEOKHWAWON GARDENING</i>

22:52.230 --> 22:53.900
A car accident!

22:53.900 --> 22:56.560
You crazy bastard!
You wanna get killed?

22:57.340 --> 22:59.900
Your eyes aren't
there for fun, asshole!

23:00.240 --> 23:01.870
I almost crashed into you!

23:04.750 --> 23:05.740
Jesus!

23:11.750 --> 23:12.950
You're good!

23:16.390 --> 23:17.720
Are you gonna apply
for art school?

23:18.530 --> 23:22.050
Doesn't it cost a lot?
Are your parents okay with it?

23:27.370 --> 23:30.170
I'm so jealous.
I'd like to study photography...

23:32.210 --> 23:34.700
But they want me to quit.
It costs too much.

23:37.980 --> 23:40.110
Hey, can you draw me?

23:41.850 --> 23:42.470
Huh?

23:42.720 --> 23:46.180
I'm supposed to draw
a self-portrait for my art class.

23:46.590 --> 23:49.250
Don't try to be so perfect.

23:49.890 --> 23:53.660
Go easy with the drawing.
Okay? How about Saturday?

23:56.400 --> 23:57.060
Okay.

23:57.300 --> 24:00.700
Really? Great! I was dying to
get out of this assignment.

24:01.340 --> 24:03.070
I'll take your photo in exchange.

24:10.240 --> 24:13.440
Wait... something's missing.

24:15.320 --> 24:16.370
Here, bite on this.

24:17.520 --> 24:18.640
Okay, that's good!

24:23.390 --> 24:27.230
And I did it again!
An artist never blames the material.

24:27.890 --> 24:29.620
Your number!
I'll send it to you.

24:39.310 --> 24:42.800
Look! Look!
There's a pervert over there!

24:44.510 --> 24:45.670
Have another drink.

24:45.750 --> 24:48.310
Stop enticing me, sweetheart.

24:49.220 --> 24:51.780
- Let me have a little squeeze.
- Not this!

24:52.320 --> 24:54.650
Jeez, that dude is totally whack!

24:57.690 --> 25:01.150
- Let's have another drink.
- Hwayi... Hwayi!

25:03.960 --> 25:04.690
You?

25:05.130 --> 25:06.230
Hwayi!

25:06.530 --> 25:07.630
You know that guy?

25:08.670 --> 25:09.330
Yeah...

25:10.940 --> 25:12.000
He's my dad.

25:13.640 --> 25:15.730
Who's that next to him?

25:15.940 --> 25:17.670
Stop drinking and driving.

25:17.740 --> 25:19.800
- It's dangerous.
- Who could it be, who?

25:19.910 --> 25:22.210
Who are you talking about?
I don't know.

25:23.950 --> 25:28.080
Wuh... want me to teach you
how to get girls?

25:28.190 --> 25:29.520
No thanks.

25:29.620 --> 25:30.450
First.

25:31.860 --> 25:32.660
Screw her.

25:33.560 --> 25:35.320
Then you're halfway there.

25:35.900 --> 25:37.870
Yeah, halfway... Just her body.

25:38.500 --> 25:43.560
Then guh... go for the kill
and grab her heart.

25:43.970 --> 25:44.870
Like how?

25:45.670 --> 25:46.870
Look carefully.

25:47.410 --> 25:50.380
This, this is the asshole.

25:50.540 --> 25:52.640
This one huh... this one's
the hole, the hole.

25:52.780 --> 25:54.770
And this one's the one
I told you about.

25:55.280 --> 25:58.550
Right here, get it real wet.

25:58.750 --> 26:01.090
And then, just do this.

26:01.220 --> 26:03.620
And go at it.

26:04.190 --> 26:09.430
Dad, dad, how come you're
always talking like that?

26:09.700 --> 26:11.960
And for a big one,
you just have to...

26:12.030 --> 26:13.190
Dad, dad...

26:13.670 --> 26:14.360
What?

26:15.700 --> 26:16.860
Aw come on...

26:19.670 --> 26:23.370
Hey, slow down a bit,
a bit, a little bit.

26:23.710 --> 26:25.180
Slow down.

26:25.510 --> 26:29.810
I'm glad I'm not driving.
My face totally shows.

26:30.050 --> 26:30.920
But dad...

26:32.050 --> 26:33.380
I'm in my school uniform.

26:35.860 --> 26:41.020
So stop wearing that uniform!
You're not even in school!

26:41.330 --> 26:44.230
They'll notice your uniform.
Loo, look down.

26:45.900 --> 26:47.460
- Hey, isn't that a high school student?
- Go, go, go.

26:48.030 --> 26:49.020
Go, go!

26:51.540 --> 26:52.370
Get them!

26:52.770 --> 26:53.760
Hurry, get in the car!

27:06.220 --> 27:09.710
If... if it was me. I... I'd have
ditched those fuckers by now.

27:14.490 --> 27:15.590
Sir, sir!

27:17.700 --> 27:19.170
Why, those sons-of-bitches!

27:26.440 --> 27:28.200
Step on the brakes and
slow the speed down.

27:29.680 --> 27:31.670
Sir, slow the speed down,
the speed!

27:32.180 --> 27:34.840
That's it, so you wanna play,
you motherfuckers?

27:35.350 --> 27:37.180
There, over there...
intersection...

27:41.220 --> 27:42.620
