01:03:25.130 --> 01:03:28.260
<i>A high school boy found
KIM Sun-ja hanging herself.</i>

01:03:29.130 --> 01:03:30.730
<i>Where's your boy?</i>

01:03:32.800 --> 01:03:35.470
<i>I'm on my way to the hospital.
I'll see you there.</i>

01:03:41.550 --> 01:03:42.280
Where's Hwayi?

01:03:43.350 --> 01:03:44.540
I don't know.

01:03:44.720 --> 01:03:47.240
When I got here, he was gone.
Aw, it's so fucking cold.

01:03:48.320 --> 01:03:49.650
Are you sure Hwayi called
the cops?

01:03:50.020 --> 01:03:53.120
Are you in denial?
What are you thinking?

01:03:54.060 --> 01:03:56.990
What about the kid?
We can't just let him run loose.

01:03:58.600 --> 01:03:59.530
And if we do?

01:04:00.160 --> 01:04:03.860
But KIM Sun-ja has seen
his face.

01:04:04.040 --> 01:04:05.870
We can't just let him
run loose like this.

01:04:06.340 --> 01:04:09.710
If she's seen him, shouldn't you
be asking what we'll do to her?

01:04:14.950 --> 01:04:17.440
Why are you doing this to me,
goddamn it...

01:04:31.300 --> 01:04:32.320
Have you found Hwayi?

01:04:33.330 --> 01:04:34.390
<i>He's not home yet?</i>

01:04:38.500 --> 01:04:39.970
A cop came by this afternoon.

01:04:44.110 --> 01:04:45.100
I'm getting a bad feeling.

01:04:45.880 --> 01:04:47.310
Once we find him
we're sending him away.

01:04:48.280 --> 01:04:49.410
<i>And what if he refuses?</i>

01:04:50.920 --> 01:04:52.470
Then I'll take him out myself!

01:04:54.320 --> 01:04:55.410
<i>We'll talk when I get home.</i>

01:05:07.030 --> 01:05:09.730
<i>JNU CONSTRUCTION INVESTIGATION
JEON SEUNG-KI...</i>

01:05:11.200 --> 01:05:12.860
Are you gonna go with me?

01:05:16.340 --> 01:05:17.140
Is that you, Hwayi?

01:05:21.650 --> 01:05:22.440
But...

01:05:24.320 --> 01:05:25.650
I don't think
I'll be able to go.

01:05:27.020 --> 01:05:28.180
What're you talking about?

01:05:30.120 --> 01:05:31.680
Where have you been?
I've been worried sick.

01:05:33.560 --> 01:05:35.030
I went back to that house.

01:05:36.590 --> 01:05:37.790
Where I killed that man.

01:05:44.000 --> 01:05:45.700
The child in the photo.

01:05:49.310 --> 01:05:50.470
Is it a child you know?

01:05:55.250 --> 01:05:58.480
Hwayi, I'm not sure
what you're thinking,

01:05:59.150 --> 01:06:01.420
- but Young-joo is all wrong.
- The child...

01:06:03.290 --> 01:06:04.410
Do you know who he is?

01:06:05.390 --> 01:06:08.520
You must be tired. We'll talk
tomorrow. Go to your room.

01:06:15.300 --> 01:06:16.200
What the hell is this?

01:06:16.470 --> 01:06:18.870
- Tell me the truth.
- About what?

01:06:20.240 --> 01:06:21.540
Who the child is.

01:06:23.810 --> 01:06:25.040
I want to know.

01:06:27.010 --> 01:06:30.880
The only thing you should
know is that I raised you.

01:06:31.750 --> 01:06:32.720
Those folks.

01:06:34.950 --> 01:06:36.720
Do you know why they
refused to leave?

01:06:38.760 --> 01:06:39.350
What?

01:06:39.860 --> 01:06:40.850
They were waiting.

01:06:43.830 --> 01:06:45.230
Just in case their child returns.

01:06:49.670 --> 01:06:50.430
Dad...

01:06:53.000 --> 01:06:54.340
You knew all along, didn't you?

01:06:56.240 --> 01:06:57.140
Put the gun down!

01:06:57.310 --> 01:06:58.300
Then why!

01:07:00.380 --> 01:07:01.510
Why didn't you stop them?

01:07:01.850 --> 01:07:03.910
I said, put the gun down!

01:07:06.420 --> 01:07:07.250
WHY?

01:07:10.020 --> 01:07:10.750
Why?

01:08:00.140 --> 01:08:01.900
<i>INCHEON HOSPITAL</i>

01:08:01.970 --> 01:08:03.370
I'll keep this short.

01:08:04.410 --> 01:08:07.500
We're tying loose ends at the hospital
and we need your help.

01:08:07.850 --> 01:08:10.870
And what about me?

01:08:12.520 --> 01:08:14.210
You think I'm your fucking dog?

01:08:14.920 --> 01:08:15.680
Detective.

01:08:16.520 --> 01:08:18.790
I don't tolerate
such filthy language.

01:08:19.260 --> 01:08:22.020
And I don't take shit from
some gang banging punk.

01:08:23.529 --> 01:08:24.120
Hey.

01:08:25.160 --> 01:08:28.790
How would it reflect on me
if you made a mess while I'm here.

01:08:28.870 --> 01:08:30.600
Tell me, PARK Ji-won,
you fuck?

01:08:31.040 --> 01:08:32.029
Come on.

01:08:33.540 --> 01:08:34.970
Who do you think I am?

01:08:36.270 --> 01:08:38.510
Just 'cause I've done some work
for you lately,

01:08:39.710 --> 01:08:42.200
you think I'm your dog?
Is that it?

01:08:56.060 --> 01:08:57.529
What a piece of crap.

01:08:58.100 --> 01:09:00.620
- Does it even work?
- Yeah.

01:09:01.600 --> 01:09:05.370
When I'm using it on fuckers
like you, mothafucka!

01:09:07.200 --> 01:09:08.640
Is your hearing okay?

01:09:09.010 --> 01:09:10.740
What's that, asshole?

01:09:21.720 --> 01:09:26.180
Tell me. Is this one
empty or not?

01:09:30.460 --> 01:09:32.399
Who do you think I am?

01:09:33.399 --> 01:09:35.130
Tell me!
Who do you think I am?

01:09:39.069 --> 01:09:42.130
What was that?
I can't hear you, speak up.

01:09:42.270 --> 01:09:44.000
Who do you think I am?

01:09:48.979 --> 01:09:53.580
You've got it all wrong.
You're not in charge. It's me.

01:09:54.490 --> 01:09:55.320
Okay?

01:10:01.690 --> 01:10:02.660
Buh, bye.

01:10:07.900 --> 01:10:09.730
Fucking asshole!

01:12:15.060 --> 01:12:15.690
Stop!

01:12:16.130 --> 01:12:16.920
Here, here.

01:12:17.060 --> 01:12:19.120
Look at that son-of-a-bitch's
timing.

01:12:20.000 --> 01:12:21.190
Can we get one from
another angle?

01:12:21.300 --> 01:12:24.390
Yes. There's one right here,
so take a look.

01:12:29.440 --> 01:12:30.340
Shit!

01:12:31.880 --> 01:12:34.540
Every fucking farm is growing
Chinese juniper trees!

01:12:35.710 --> 01:12:37.610
Why does it have to be
Chinese junipers...

01:12:38.550 --> 01:12:39.350
Fucking shit...

01:12:40.220 --> 01:12:42.020
Why can't it be something
more rare.

01:13:01.510 --> 01:13:03.530
<i>PEACE NURSING HOME</i>

01:13:29.800 --> 01:13:30.890
Thank you.

01:13:39.280 --> 01:13:40.240
It's done.

01:13:45.380 --> 01:13:46.180
Thank you.

01:13:49.920 --> 01:13:52.820
It's just for one day.

01:13:57.190 --> 01:13:58.590
Why are you out here?

01:13:59.430 --> 01:14:00.490
Go inside.

01:14:04.030 --> 01:14:05.090
What's wrong?

01:14:05.740 --> 01:14:08.470
Didn't you say she's your mom?
You're not gonna go inside?

01:15:03.060 --> 01:15:05.190
Muh... mom...

01:15:12.540 --> 01:15:13.530
Mom...

01:16:41.190 --> 01:16:41.850
So...

01:16:43.530 --> 01:16:44.620
You wanna kill me too?

01:16:48.670 --> 01:16:49.830
Then you'll need one clean shot.

01:16:51.100 --> 01:16:52.690
Or else you're 100% dead.

01:17:11.520 --> 01:17:15.080
I heard you saved KIM Sun-ja
and killed Jin-sung.

01:17:16.630 --> 01:17:17.530
What's with you?

01:17:18.630 --> 01:17:20.690
We're the only ones
in your memory.

01:17:23.000 --> 01:17:24.700
KIM Sun-ja's gonna die anyway.

01:17:25.840 --> 01:17:27.330
Leave her alone!

01:17:31.210 --> 01:17:32.540
I'll kill them.

01:17:33.410 --> 01:17:36.070
Mr. JEON, the Incheon people...

01:17:37.950 --> 01:17:40.510
I'll... I'll kill them all.

01:17:41.050 --> 01:17:41.710
You?

01:17:43.020 --> 01:17:43.890
Think wisely.

01:17:44.860 --> 01:17:46.920
KIM Sun-ja must die
in order for you to live.

01:18:09.680 --> 01:18:10.650
Hwayi...

01:18:17.720 --> 01:18:18.690
Hwayi...

01:18:27.500 --> 01:18:28.430
Hwayi!

01:18:29.670 --> 01:18:30.400
Hwayi!

01:18:37.310 --> 01:18:39.110
You're not really gonna shoot,
are you?

01:18:58.630 --> 01:19:01.430
Come on. Can't catch him?
You want me to drive?

01:19:10.610 --> 01:19:11.770
Don't shoot!

01:19:15.450 --> 01:19:17.440
I... I... I'll... catch him.

01:19:44.140 --> 01:19:44.970
Hwayi...

01:19:45.080 --> 01:19:45.840
Wait!

01:20:07.830 --> 01:20:11.230
Hwayi! Hwayi! Talk to me!

01:20:11.400 --> 01:20:13.430
Let's talk! I'll listen!

01:20:14.270 --> 01:20:17.000
Hwayi! Hwayi!

01:20:17.710 --> 01:20:18.680
Hwayi!

01:20:58.620 --> 01:21:01.280
That's enough. Now get him.

01:21:22.670 --> 01:21:24.040
Gotcha! Step on it!

01:21:59.410 --> 01:22:02.210
He was intending to
kill us, right?

01:22:03.010 --> 01:22:04.170
- Yeah.
- What?

01:22:06.120 --> 01:22:08.020
I tuh... taught him to do that.

01:22:12.720 --> 01:22:14.720
<i>DAY BREAKERS CASE
DON'T TOUCH!</i>

01:22:14.890 --> 01:22:15.980
Fucking moron!

01:22:17.630 --> 01:22:18.720
You crazy bastard!

01:22:43.350 --> 01:22:46.380
<i>RANSOM NOTE
$1 MILLION, 3/24 AT 14:20
SUBWAY LINE 3, YANGJAE</i>

01:23:32.940 --> 01:23:33.700
Is that you, Hwayi?

01:23:35.710 --> 01:23:37.000
<i>I need to ask you something.</i>

01:23:40.080 --> 01:23:41.670
<i>Why did you raise me?</i>

01:23:44.480 --> 01:23:46.070
What kind of question is that?
I'm your dad.

01:23:51.120 --> 01:23:52.110
Where are you now?

01:23:54.390 --> 01:23:55.220
<i>Dad...</i>

01:23:57.290 --> 01:23:59.260
<i>Are you gonna come to get me?</i>

01:24:02.630 --> 01:24:03.500
Of course.

01:24:04.970 --> 01:24:09.340
The place you first took me to.
Bring everyone there by 10 am.

01:24:09.970 --> 01:24:11.000
I'll be waiting.

01:25:08.000 --> 01:25:09.130
Did you want to see me, sir?

01:25:10.830 --> 01:25:14.000
What happened last night?

01:25:15.510 --> 01:25:18.910
Sir, we had a small setback,
but we'll fix things soon.

01:25:22.080 --> 01:25:23.980
The security guard
gave this to me.

01:25:28.520 --> 01:25:30.180
<i>IF YOU WANT KIM SUN-JA
BRING 5 TIMES THE BALANCE</i>

01:25:30.290 --> 01:25:31.810
<i>TO THE SUNGJI CEMENT
FACTORY BY 9AM TODAY</i>

01:25:31.890 --> 01:25:34.380
Why are these people
doing this to me?

01:25:41.130 --> 01:25:48.000
I never make any enemies...
You know that, right?

01:25:50.140 --> 01:25:51.010
Yes, sir.

01:26:07.160 --> 01:26:09.890
What's this?
Are we having a party?

01:26:13.060 --> 01:26:14.360
You should look out
here for him.

01:26:14.930 --> 01:26:17.200
Nuh, nuh, no, no.
I... I wanna go with you.

01:26:17.770 --> 01:26:18.890
Do as Beom-soo says.

01:26:24.940 --> 01:26:27.780
Duh... don't kill him. Okay?

01:26:41.320 --> 01:26:42.490
You're late.

01:26:44.390 --> 01:26:45.690
This way, please.

01:26:51.670 --> 01:26:55.110
Aw, don't be rude.
Put your guns away.

01:26:59.110 --> 01:27:01.910
I can tell from this place that

01:27:02.610 --> 01:27:04.880
you've got
quite a romantic side to you.

01:27:05.550 --> 01:27:08.420
But I must say
it's not my taste.

01:27:11.920 --> 01:27:13.120
What's so funny?

01:27:13.460 --> 01:27:14.820
We didn't call you here.

01:27:17.260 --> 01:27:18.730
That won't do.

01:27:20.000 --> 01:27:23.260
I've quintupled the balance
as you demanded.

01:27:23.470 --> 01:27:25.130
So hand KIM Sun-ja over to us.

01:27:26.470 --> 01:27:27.960
Who admitted this woman?

01:27:28.570 --> 01:27:30.470
She said she was her daughter.

01:27:31.170 --> 01:27:32.840
She was here a few minutes ago.

01:27:33.280 --> 01:27:34.070
What's all this?

01:27:34.140 --> 01:27:35.170
<i>MS. YANG,
FEMALE, AGE 55</i>

01:27:35.250 --> 01:27:37.150
Is this all some kind of act?

01:27:38.580 --> 01:27:40.980
So you didn't send this?

01:27:42.890 --> 01:27:46.120
There's a number here.
Shall I try calling it?

01:28:07.210 --> 01:28:11.440
What is this? Just tell him
to come inside.

01:32:12.560 --> 01:32:15.390
I found KIM Sun-ja. If you're
whacking her, get over here.

01:32:17.060 --> 01:32:19.590
Hey, PARK Ji-won,
are you listening?

01:32:21.730 --> 01:32:22.560
Where are you?

01:32:24.500 --> 01:32:25.260
Suk-tae?

01:32:57.470 --> 01:32:58.560
Hwuh... Hwayi!

01:33:04.870 --> 01:33:07.070
- Hwayi.
- Let go. Let go!

01:33:08.510 --> 01:33:10.210
Stop... stop it.

01:33:11.780 --> 01:33:13.650
You're just like them!

01:33:15.520 --> 01:33:18.420
I... I'm here,
duh, dad's here...

01:33:19.060 --> 01:33:22.290
You're just the same.
You fooled me like the others!

01:33:22.660 --> 01:33:24.290
That's enough now.
Just stop...

01:33:24.390 --> 01:33:29.830
Why should I? Why!
Why should I stop!

01:33:30.900 --> 01:33:33.340
Dad will hold you, okay?

01:33:33.740 --> 01:33:35.730
No! You're just like them!

01:33:36.210 --> 01:33:38.440
Go away! Go!

01:33:38.880 --> 01:33:40.000
GO AWAY!

01:34:02.800 --> 01:34:04.200
Ah... Jeez...

01:34:10.840 --> 01:34:12.140
Hwuh... Hwayi...

01:34:13.540 --> 01:34:14.370
Dad...

01:34:15.710 --> 01:34:22.280
I... I'm so suh, sorry... Hwayi.

01:34:23.250 --> 01:34:24.980
Dad! No... no!

01:34:26.020 --> 01:34:28.080
I... I'm really really sorry...

01:34:28.960 --> 01:34:31.330
Hwayi... dad's so sorry for...

01:34:32.330 --> 01:34:33.350
DAD!

01:34:52.380 --> 01:34:53.470
Dad...

01:35:25.780 --> 01:35:30.740
Hwayi, it's me. Some men are
looking for you.

01:35:31.150 --> 01:35:32.090
<i>What should I do?</i>

01:35:41.100 --> 01:35:42.660
Hey, are you listening?

01:35:46.640 --> 01:35:48.200
Someone's inside.

01:35:48.470 --> 01:35:50.500
I know, you fucking bitch!
Open the goddamn door!

01:35:52.070 --> 01:35:52.940
Open the door!

01:35:59.320 --> 01:36:00.340
Police.

01:36:02.490 --> 01:36:03.710
May I come in?

01:36:11.330 --> 01:36:13.090
What the fuck!

01:36:13.260 --> 01:36:14.360
Hey, you asshole!

01:36:24.140 --> 01:36:25.540
Who is this child?

01:36:27.540 --> 01:36:29.030
Who is this kid here?

01:36:32.210 --> 01:36:32.980
My son.

01:36:34.420 --> 01:36:36.320
- Your son?
- Yes...

01:36:37.690 --> 01:36:38.450
My son.

01:36:42.020 --> 01:36:43.120
Ms. JANG Young-joo?

01:36:44.630 --> 01:36:47.760
You're JANG Young-joo,
right? Born in 1971.

01:36:48.760 --> 01:36:50.430
The owner of this house.

01:36:50.730 --> 01:36:52.430
Your husband is YOON Suk-tae.

01:36:52.500 --> 01:36:55.100
Your housemates are
YOON Ki-tae, LEE Jin-sung.

01:36:55.910 --> 01:36:57.070
I don't see a son though.

01:37:01.440 --> 01:37:04.180
He died. Two years ago.

01:37:05.250 --> 01:37:06.680
Is that so?

01:37:09.250 --> 01:37:12.380
I'm looking for these guys
called the Day Breakers.

01:37:13.060 --> 01:37:16.990
This time they killed this man
named IM Hyung-taek.

01:37:20.030 --> 01:37:22.160
They're known to be cold
and methodical.

01:37:23.800 --> 01:37:25.360
So why so many bullets?

01:37:27.540 --> 01:37:28.770
And traces of hesitation.

01:37:32.210 --> 01:37:35.410
This could mean
the killer knows the victim.

01:37:38.480 --> 01:37:41.920
Please get to the point
and leave.

01:37:43.520 --> 01:37:45.420
You know IM Hyung-taek,
don't you?

01:37:48.760 --> 01:37:51.060
- I don't.
- You don't?

01:37:55.870 --> 01:37:58.800
YOON Suk-tae, YOON Ki-tae
and JANG Young-joo.

01:38:00.200 --> 01:38:02.400
You all grew up at the Sungji
Orphanage in Incheon.

01:38:03.640 --> 01:38:07.340
IM Hyung-taek's father was
the foundation's Chief Director.

01:38:08.880 --> 01:38:10.470
Think carefully.

01:38:12.350 --> 01:38:13.610
Are you sure you don't know?

01:38:25.190 --> 01:38:29.130
That's why you gotta make
friends with the right people.

01:38:30.230 --> 01:38:33.290
I wasn't always a bad person,
you know?

01:38:34.340 --> 01:38:40.140
But... Shit...
I made the wrong friends.

01:38:41.010 --> 01:38:43.040
And now I'm in deep shit.

01:38:44.350 --> 01:38:46.370
You startled me,
you fucking asshole!

01:38:49.750 --> 01:38:50.620
What about the kid?

01:38:51.520 --> 01:38:52.250
Did you kill him?

01:38:55.190 --> 01:38:56.320
She's on the 4th floor.

01:38:57.130 --> 01:38:59.930
I've cleared the ward for
the job, so go get...

01:39:05.100 --> 01:39:05.930
What?

01:39:09.210 --> 01:39:10.940
Aw shit...

01:40:31.520 --> 01:40:34.650
These fuckers are
the Day Breakers, right?

01:40:36.830 --> 01:40:37.660
Get out.

01:40:38.260 --> 01:40:39.790
You people also killed
IM Hyung-taek, right?

01:40:42.330 --> 01:40:45.060
Who's this kid?
The student at the crime scene.

01:40:45.940 --> 01:40:47.160
He's was in it as well,
wasn't he?

01:40:48.370 --> 01:40:49.570
The kid's not dead, is he?

01:40:51.210 --> 01:40:52.040
Hwayi...

01:40:52.880 --> 01:40:56.440
Hwayi's a good boy.
It's not his fault.

01:40:57.280 --> 01:40:57.970
Hwayi?

01:41:02.080 --> 01:41:02.920
Hwayi tree...

01:41:04.650 --> 01:41:06.140
What the fuck...

01:41:11.860 --> 01:41:12.790
Did you people...

01:41:15.100 --> 01:41:16.220
really raise the kid?

01:41:19.340 --> 01:41:21.900
You never saw him
grow up, did you?

01:41:24.140 --> 01:41:25.440
He was about this tall at first.

01:41:27.210 --> 01:41:27.970
Now he's...

01:41:29.180 --> 01:41:30.610
Ah, but you've
seen him before, right?

01:41:34.650 --> 01:41:36.210
He's a good kid.

01:41:38.550 --> 01:41:39.920
And mighty bright.

01:41:41.190 --> 01:41:42.720
Whatever he's taught,
he learns fast.

01:41:43.730 --> 01:41:44.920
He's good at drawing, too.

01:41:48.160 --> 01:41:51.790
He's such a great kid,

01:41:53.570 --> 01:41:54.660
but he has this sickness.

01:41:56.810 --> 01:42:00.610
He keeps on seeing things.
When it's bad, he has fits.

01:42:02.340 --> 01:42:03.330
It's heartbreaking to watch.

01:42:07.950 --> 01:42:09.480
I guess he takes that after me.

01:42:13.020 --> 01:42:14.220
I used to be like that.

01:42:16.290 --> 01:42:17.160
Don't come near!

01:42:17.930 --> 01:42:19.990
Or I'll kill you...
Don't come near...

